com.google.api.client.json.jackson2

Class JacksonGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.json.JsonGenerator
      • com.google.api.client.json.jackson2.JacksonGenerator

  • final class JacksonGenerator
extends JsonGenerator
    Low-level JSON serializer implementation based on Jackson.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.

    Author:
    Yaniv Inbar
